    + Stop exclude git and travis hint files when repackaging source.
    + Add Files section for packaging,
      and corresponding License section.
  * Update watch file:
    + Bump watch file format version to 4.
    + Add usage comment.
    + Use substitution strings.
    + Track tags (not releases).
    + Drop unneeded uversionmangle.
    + Generalize dversionmangle.
    + Bump repacksuffix.
